edu.rit.m2mi.life3

Packages that use edu.rit.m2mi.life3
edu.rit.m2mi.life3 Package edu.rit.m2mi.life3 is a program for John Horton Conway's Game of Life using M2MI. 
 

Classes in edu.rit.m2mi.life3 used by edu.rit.m2mi.life3
LifeCell
          Interface LifeCell specifies the interface for an exported object that encapsulates a cell in the Game of Life (version 3).
LifeCellListener
          Interface LifeCellListener specifies the interface for an exported object that listens to cell state reports in the Game of Life (version 3).
LifeController
          Interface LifeController specifies the interface for an object that controls the computation in the Game of Life (version 3).
